<p>inspected, CTI attends the &#8220;great majority&#8221;. CTI officials stated they were able to attend 95 per cent 
of crime scenes. CTI was unable to attend the other 5 per cent because of a lack of transportation, 
danger (e.g., ongoing conflict) or difficulty in reaching the site because of terrain and geography. 
According to the military, its facilitation of CTI investigations can cost US$ 8,000 per case. 
</p>
