</p>
<p>peace law: initial stages in the demobilization of AUC and first judicial proceedings, document 
OEA/Ser.L/V/II, according to which, of 28,000 people initially demobilized, approximately 90 per 
cent failed to offer &#8220;significant&#8221; information about crimes committed. 
</p>
